| Day       | Time (Suggested) | Duration | Meeting Type  | Purpose |
|-----------|------------------|----------|---------------|---------|
| **Monday**    | 10:00 AM          | 15 min   | Monday Standup        | Share goals and updates for the upcoming work week |
| **Wednesday** | 10:00 AM          | 15 min   | Midweek Standup| Quick check-in on progress and issues. |
| **Thursday**   | 6:30‚Äì7:30 PM    | 15 - 60 min   | In-person sprint Review & Planning | Review completed work and modify sprint plan if necessary. |
| **Friday**    | 10:00 AM          | 15 min   | End-of-Week Standup | Summarize progress, identify pending tasks, and prep for the next week. |

> ‚è±Ô∏è Total meeting time per week: **60 - 105 minutes**
